00:25:03,380 --> 00:25:04,940
So when will you end it?

551
00:25:06,180 --> 00:25:07,020
Soon.

552
00:25:07,180 --> 00:25:08,380
Tomorrow, probably.

553
00:25:08,380 --> 00:25:09,940
You will reconcile with him?

554
00:25:10,180 --> 00:25:11,020
No.

555
00:25:11,180 --> 00:25:13,940
The list of transferred employees
will be announced tomorrow.

556
00:25:14,020 --> 00:25:16,380
By then,
Zheng Hao and his parents will know that

557
00:25:16,380 --> 00:25:17,700
I haven't withdrawn my application.

558
00:25:17,860 --> 00:25:19,940
I guess this cold war will end anyway.

559
00:25:19,940 --> 00:25:22,380
So what will result from this cold war?

560
00:25:22,380 --> 00:25:23,900
Breaking up or peace?

561
00:25:24,940 --> 00:25:26,420
I haven't figured it out yet.

562
00:25:28,940 --> 00:25:30,780
I just want to leave this place.

563
00:25:32,020 --> 00:25:33,140
Stop talking about me.

564
00:25:33,140 --> 00:25:34,620
When will your flight arrive?

565
00:25:35,140 --> 00:25:38,180
Friday evening, my time.

566
00:25:38,500 --> 00:25:40,140
Saturday morning, Beijing time.

567
00:25:40,140 --> 00:25:41,690
I'll see you this Saturday night.

568
00:25:42,700 --> 00:25:44,420
I miss you so much.

569
00:25:44,420 --> 00:25:45,900
Xiuya!

570
00:25:46,080 --> 00:25:46,920
Me too.

571
00:25:47,480 --> 00:25:48,780
Then let's meet this Saturday.

572
00:25:48,780 --> 00:25:51,180
Text me before you board the plane.

573
00:25:52,660 --> 00:25:54,700
Get some sleep. It's getting late.

574
00:25:54,900 --> 00:25:55,940
Okay, bye.

575
00:25:56,080 --> 00:25:56,940
Good night.

