587
00:26:41,620 --> 00:26:44,900
(Corporate Communication Department
Gao Jie Duan Xiaowei)

588
00:26:48,140 --> 00:26:48,980
Manager Hu.

589
00:26:49,380 --> 00:26:50,220
Manager.

590
00:26:50,380 --> 00:26:51,700
Zheng Hao didn't ask for my opinion.

591
00:26:51,700 --> 00:26:53,420
He went to you on his own initiative.

592
00:26:53,700 --> 00:26:55,420
I asked him. He said you two have talked.

593
00:26:55,420 --> 00:26:56,620
And you've agreed.

594
00:26:56,620 --> 00:26:58,020
How can I take it back now?

595
00:26:58,220 --> 00:26:59,420
There's nothing I can do.

596
00:26:59,900 --> 00:27:02,220
But Zheng Hao doesn't represent me.

597
00:27:02,960 --> 00:27:03,800
Manager.

598
00:27:07,260 --> 00:27:08,100
Xiuya.

599
00:27:09,020 --> 00:27:10,820
You were upset about the previous incident.

600
00:27:11,500 --> 00:27:13,300
But it just happens at work.

601
00:27:14,020 --> 00:27:16,260
I think Zheng Hao did it for your own good.

602
00:27:17,050 --> 00:27:18,060
You shouldn't be so headstrong.

603
00:27:18,380 --> 00:27:19,740
You've put me at an awkward place.

604
00:27:20,020 --> 00:27:20,880
And you can't

605
00:27:20,890 --> 00:27:22,900
just throw away your own future for this.

606
00:27:24,540 --> 00:27:25,820
Why must you cause such a scene?

607
00:27:26,580 --> 00:27:27,740
Think about it.

608
00:27:29,780 --> 00:27:30,620
Everyone is here.

609
00:27:31,260 --> 00:27:32,500
This task is about

610
00:27:32,500 --> 00:27:33,820
our exclusive interview.

611
00:27:34,300 --> 00:27:35,260
On our official account,

612
00:27:35,260 --> 00:27:37,580
we'll open a new National Day special column.

613
00:27:53,820 --> 00:27:55,260
Did you care about how I feel?

614
00:27:55,260 --> 00:27:56,500
Of course, I do.

615
00:27:56,500 --> 00:27:57,340
Haven't we made it clear

616
00:27:57,360 --> 00:27:58,820
at dinner the other day?

617
00:27:58,820 --> 00:28:00,340
Everyone agreed to this.

618
00:28:00,340 --> 00:28:01,960
Agreed to what?

619
00:28:01,960 --> 00:28:03,100
Haven't you agreed that I should...

620
00:28:03,260 --> 00:28:04,580
It's you who keep saying that.

621
00:28:06,340 --> 00:28:08,060
It'll just take a year.

622
00:28:08,060 --> 00:28:10,420
One year. One year is long enough.

623
00:28:10,660 --> 00:28:12,660
(Zhonghe Real Estate)
You can't keep making decisions for me.

624
00:28:12,660 --> 00:28:14,060
It's not respectful.

625
00:28:14,060 --> 00:28:15,300
So you're being respectful?

626
00:28:15,300 --> 00:28:16,580
You promised my mom.

627
00:28:16,580 --> 00:28:18,300
Then what?
Did you go to Ms. Hu to withdraw it?

628
00:28:18,300 --> 00:28:19,500
I didn't promise your mom.

629
00:28:19,500 --> 00:28:20,580
I said I'd think about it.

630
00:28:20,580 --> 00:28:22,300
If you say you'd think about it,

631
00:28:22,300 --> 00:28:23,260
it means you have agreed.

632
00:28:23,260 --> 00:28:24,160
You only put it that way

633
00:28:24,160 --> 00:28:25,440
because you don't want to be embarrassed.

634
00:28:25,450 --> 00:28:27,660
No, it means that I haven't agreed.

635
00:28:27,660 --> 00:28:30,040
It means the decision is up to me.

636
00:28:30,050 --> 00:28:31,500
I only said that

637
00:28:31,510 --> 00:28:33,680
because I didn't want to embarrass your mom.

638
00:28:34,580 --> 00:28:35,760
I don't want to talk to you anymore.

639
00:28:35,770 --> 00:28:36,820
Go away. I need some time alone.

640
00:28:36,820 --> 00:28:38,120
Fine. Calm yourself.

641
00:28:38,130 --> 00:28:39,740
Think about it tonight.

642
00:28:40,700 --> 00:28:41,740
I'll pick you up at 4:00 PM tomorrow.

643
00:28:41,740 --> 00:28:42,580
For Zhang Yan's wedding.

644
00:28:43,100 --> 00:28:43,940
I don't want to go.

645
00:28:44,060 --> 00:28:46,100
We had the plan. You must go.

646
00:28:47,740 --> 00:28:48,820
Bad timing.

647
00:28:55,020 --> 00:28:56,760
Why is she like a different person?

648
00:28:56,780 --> 00:28:58,780
(Does Zheng Hao really don't understand)

649
00:28:58,790 --> 00:28:59,900
(what Xiuya means,)

650
00:29:00,380 --> 00:29:01,500
(or is he only willing to)

651
00:29:01,500 --> 00:29:03,740
(interpret her words
according to his subjective view.)

652
00:29:04,260 --> 00:29:05,500
(So is Xiuya upset)

653
00:29:05,780 --> 00:29:08,300
(because he interprets the words
too arbitrarily)

654
00:29:08,660 --> 00:29:10,580
(or because she's not straightforward enough?)

655
00:29:11,060 --> 00:29:13,060
Hold a hand bouquet in front of your chest.

656
00:29:13,500 --> 00:29:15,020
Walk ahead to welcome the bride.

657
00:29:15,020 --> 00:29:17,020
- Keep your head up.
- Okay.

658
00:29:17,020 --> 00:29:18,580
- Remind me if I crouch my back.
- Okay.

659
00:29:18,780 --> 00:29:20,060
Just show your best self.

660
00:29:20,060 --> 00:29:22,340
Then the bride waits for you there.

661
00:29:22,580 --> 00:29:23,500
And when you get there,

662
00:29:23,500 --> 00:29:24,820
stand still. We'll play the music.

663
00:29:24,820 --> 00:29:25,900
And walk this way.

664
00:29:25,900 --> 00:29:27,740
- That's the whole process, okay?
- Okay.

665
00:29:27,740 --> 00:29:28,820
- Go ahead.
- Sure.

666
00:29:28,820 --> 00:29:29,740
- Okay.
- Thanks.

667
00:29:43,820 --> 00:29:44,660
Having a fight?

668
00:29:46,740 --> 00:29:47,580
No.

669
00:29:48,580 --> 00:29:50,580
I saw you two on my way here.

670
00:29:50,580 --> 00:29:52,100
You were arguing on the street.

671
00:29:55,300 --> 00:29:57,100
Be honest with me.

672
00:29:57,780 --> 00:29:59,580
Are you having an affair?

673
00:30:00,500 --> 00:30:01,340
You're full of bullshit.

674
00:30:03,300 --> 00:30:04,340
No, I'm not.

675
00:30:07,200 --> 00:30:08,040
Lower your voice.

676
00:30:10,100 --> 00:30:11,340
You don't know about me?

677
00:30:13,300 --> 00:30:15,100
I can't see through a person's pretense.

678
00:30:15,780 --> 00:30:16,620
No...

679
00:30:16,820 --> 00:30:20,260
I just think sister-in-law
has a good personality.

680
00:30:20,260 --> 00:30:22,020
You made her so mad.

681
00:30:22,600 --> 00:30:24,060
It must be a huge mistake.

682
00:30:24,710 --> 00:30:25,900
It's not a big deal.

683
00:30:26,730 --> 00:30:28,300
I just didn't tell her that

684
00:30:28,300 --> 00:30:30,500
I asked her boss to solve her problem for her.

685
00:30:31,260 --> 00:30:32,580
Maybe she feel embarrassed.

686
00:30:32,820 --> 00:30:33,660
What's more?

687
00:30:34,010 --> 00:30:35,260
There's nothing more to it.

688
00:30:37,420 --> 00:30:39,060
Well, this is not so bad.

689
00:30:39,260 --> 00:30:40,820
Yeah, I think so.

690
00:30:41,160 --> 00:30:42,340
I don't know what's wrong with her.

691
00:30:42,340 --> 00:30:44,060
She's like
a completely different person lately.

692
00:30:48,540 --> 00:30:51,660
I don't know if I'm supposed to say this.

693
00:30:52,660 --> 00:30:54,300
Where did you pick up this gibberish?

694
00:30:54,300 --> 00:30:55,540
If you don't know, then shut up.

695
00:30:56,100 --> 00:30:57,300
But I can't hold it back.

696
00:30:57,300 --> 00:30:58,140
Then speak up.

697
00:30:59,160 --> 00:31:02,100
I think you treat her too well.

698
00:31:02,290 --> 00:31:03,540
You spoiled her.

699
00:31:03,820 --> 00:31:05,060
She can't even find her way around.

700
00:31:05,380 --> 00:31:06,540
Listen to me.

701
00:31:06,790 --> 00:31:08,300
Ignore her today.

702
00:31:08,680 --> 00:31:09,540
Just let her be.

703
00:31:10,020 --> 00:31:11,820
Or else, it will be tough
for you in the future.

704
00:31:13,300 --> 00:31:15,540
I noticed that you've learned
a lot of cunning tricks

705
00:31:15,540 --> 00:31:16,820
really fast lately.

706
00:31:17,130 --> 00:31:18,540
I'm getting married tomorrow.

707
00:31:18,980 --> 00:31:21,060
If I don't learn fast, I'll be bullied.

708
00:31:22,900 --> 00:31:25,340
So, is she still coming tomorrow?

709
00:31:25,820 --> 00:31:27,300
Are we still going to do it?

710
00:31:27,300 --> 00:31:28,140
Sure.

711
00:31:28,540 --> 00:31:30,300
We planned for it. We have to do it.

712
00:31:31,260 --> 00:31:32,100
Then that's fine.

713
00:31:33,820 --> 00:31:35,300
If we don't do it, I...

714
00:31:35,900 --> 00:31:37,300
I don't even want to get married.

715
00:31:38,620 --> 00:31:41,480
We have to be the stars of my wedding.

716
00:31:43,260 --> 00:31:45,300
Bro, it's fine for you to say this before me.

717
00:31:45,300 --> 00:31:46,780
Don't let your wife hear this, okay?

718
00:31:50,300 --> 00:31:51,140
It's fine.

719
00:32:10,020 --> 00:32:11,740
Hello, please throw the ball back to us.

720
00:32:14,260 --> 00:32:15,300
Why don't you join us?

721
00:32:16,260 --> 00:32:17,500
No, take your time.

722
00:32:17,740 --> 00:32:18,580
Fine.

723
00:32:35,390 --> 00:32:36,230
Xiuya.

724
00:32:46,300 --> 00:32:47,140
Hello.

725
00:32:47,300 --> 00:32:49,020
Hey, where are you? You're not home?

726
00:32:50,500 --> 00:32:51,340
You're at my place?

727
00:32:51,400 --> 00:32:52,540
Didn't I tell you that

728
00:32:52,540 --> 00:32:54,820
I'd pick you up at 4:00 PM
to go to Zhang Yan's wedding?

729
00:32:55,300 --> 00:32:56,820
Didn't I tell you that I wasn't going?

730
00:32:57,250 --> 00:32:59,440
Didn't I tell you that you must go?

731
00:33:00,020 --> 00:33:01,100
Where are you now?

732
00:33:01,580 --> 00:33:03,060
I'm out for a walk.

733
00:33:03,300 --> 00:33:06,100
Zheng Hao, I'm really not in the mood.

734
00:33:06,100 --> 00:33:07,260
Go by yourself.

735
00:33:07,660 --> 00:33:08,820
No, you must go.

736
00:33:09,100 --> 00:33:10,500
If you don't go today,

737
00:33:10,500 --> 00:33:12,180
you embarrass me in front of

738
00:33:12,180 --> 00:33:13,260
my best friends and colleagues.

739
00:33:13,260 --> 00:33:15,060
Zhang Yan will think you don't like him.

740
00:33:15,060 --> 00:33:16,580
He's the Chairman's nephew.

741
00:33:17,060 --> 00:33:18,540
How can you expect us to get along?

742
00:33:18,820 --> 00:33:21,060
Besides, many leaders and the Chairman

743
00:33:21,060 --> 00:33:22,020
will be there today.

744
00:33:22,040 --> 00:33:23,660
If they see that
I can't even command my girlfriend,

745
00:33:23,660 --> 00:33:24,820
how can I command my team?

746
00:33:24,820 --> 00:33:26,500
(Wu Xiuya listens to
Zheng Hao's exasperated voice)

747
00:33:26,500 --> 00:33:28,300
(coming from the other end of the phone.)

748
00:33:28,580 --> 00:33:29,780
(She recalls all the argument)

749
00:33:29,780 --> 00:33:31,540
(she had with him recently.)

750
00:33:31,820 --> 00:33:33,300
(She suddenly feels so tired.)

751
00:33:33,580 --> 00:33:35,580
(She no longer wants to argue with Zheng Hao.)

752
00:33:36,500 --> 00:33:37,820
Okay, I'll go back now.

753
00:33:38,060 --> 00:33:40,060
It's too late.
Send me a location and I'll pick you up.

754
00:33:40,540 --> 00:33:42,660
But I have to get changed and put on makeup.

755
00:33:42,900 --> 00:33:44,060
It's too late.

756
00:33:44,180 --> 00:33:45,900
Don't move. I'll pick you up now.

757
00:33:55,150 --> 00:33:56,060
Congratulations!

758
00:33:56,060 --> 00:33:57,060
Thank you.

759
00:33:58,100 --> 00:33:59,060
You go in first.

760
00:33:59,060 --> 00:33:59,940
Go ahead. Get some rest.

761
00:33:59,940 --> 00:34:01,020
Here. Look at the camera.

762
00:34:01,300 --> 00:34:03,260
One, two, three, okay.

763
00:34:03,260 --> 00:34:04,580
- Congratulations!
- Go in first.

764
00:34:04,580 --> 00:34:05,820
Happy wedding!

765
00:34:06,580 --> 00:34:08,060
Careful. This way.

766
00:34:13,340 --> 00:34:14,580
Hello, Chairman.

767
00:34:16,900 --> 00:34:18,300
Hello, Chairman.

768
00:34:18,420 --> 00:34:20,580
Chairman, our seats are over there.

769
00:34:21,020 --> 00:34:23,060
- Okay.
- Hello, Chairman.

770
00:34:23,780 --> 00:34:24,620
Get seated.

771
00:34:24,620 --> 00:34:26,220
Hello, Chairman.

772
00:34:26,620 --> 00:34:28,020
Hello, Chairman.

773
00:34:45,540 --> 00:34:46,500
Slow down.

774
00:34:46,500 --> 00:34:47,900
We'd be late if we slow down.

775
00:34:57,780 --> 00:34:58,860
Zheng Hao, take the seat.

776
00:34:58,860 --> 00:35:00,060
I need to greet the Chairman.

777
00:35:00,060 --> 00:35:00,900
Hurry up.

778
00:35:01,650 --> 00:35:02,860
What are you doing? Come with me.

779
00:35:03,080 --> 00:35:04,520
I'm not going. I'm not properly dressed.

780
00:35:05,350 --> 00:35:06,600
You must go.

781
00:35:07,340 --> 00:35:08,780
Women age like fine wine.

782
00:35:09,790 --> 00:35:10,660
I was wrong.

783
00:35:11,500 --> 00:35:12,340
Chairman.

784
00:35:12,690 --> 00:35:13,860
I came to say hello.

785
00:35:15,020 --> 00:35:16,270
Zheng, what took you so long?

786
00:35:16,280 --> 00:35:17,360
I was stuck in traffic.

787
00:35:17,580 --> 00:35:19,280
Hello, Chairman, I'm from the CCD...

788
00:35:19,500 --> 00:35:21,500
So she's with you?

789
00:35:21,500 --> 00:35:22,620
Yes, she's my girlfriend.

790
00:35:23,160 --> 00:35:24,780
Your talent and her beauty
make a perfect couple.

791
00:35:24,980 --> 00:35:25,860
Thank you.

792
00:35:25,860 --> 00:35:26,700
Zheng.

793
00:35:26,710 --> 00:35:29,020
You girlfriend has a marketable face.

794
00:35:29,620 --> 00:35:31,340
Do you think so?

795
00:35:31,340 --> 00:35:32,820
Yes, she's so pretty.

796
00:35:33,420 --> 00:35:34,260
Zheng.

797
00:35:34,420 --> 00:35:36,860
You're dressed very formally today.

798
00:35:37,060 --> 00:35:38,060
I'm the best man today.

799
00:35:38,060 --> 00:35:39,020
I'll be on stage later.

800
00:35:39,370 --> 00:35:40,220
Mr. Li.

801
00:35:40,220 --> 00:35:41,340
You're going on stage too?

802
00:35:41,860 --> 00:35:42,700
What a coincidence!

803
00:35:42,900 --> 00:35:44,500
Dear distinguished guests.

804
00:35:44,500 --> 00:35:46,010
- It's starting. We'll go now.
- Ladies and gentlemen.

805
00:35:46,020 --> 00:35:48,500
Family and friends.

806
00:35:48,720 --> 00:35:50,600
Good evening.

807
00:35:50,880 --> 00:35:51,980
Great.

808
00:35:53,060 --> 00:35:54,860
Enjoy your time. I have to help.

809
00:35:55,340 --> 00:35:58,020
On this joyous occasion for the newlyweds,

810
00:35:58,200 --> 00:35:59,480
we meet here

811
00:35:59,540 --> 00:36:01,580
in the hall the Garden Hotel

812
00:36:01,900 --> 00:36:03,700
surrounded by blooming flowers

813
00:36:03,700 --> 00:36:05,580
for celebration.

814
00:36:05,800 --> 00:36:07,900
We celebrate together

815
00:36:07,900 --> 00:36:09,830
for the newlyweds' wedding today.

816
00:36:10,140 --> 00:36:12,500
Friends, this cup of red wine

817
00:36:12,500 --> 00:36:14,460
is brewed by the newlyweds

818
00:36:14,460 --> 00:36:16,580
with their love and affection.

819
00:36:16,780 --> 00:36:18,540
Only those who truly love each other

820
00:36:18,540 --> 00:36:21,060
can taste such sweet wine.

821
00:36:21,060 --> 00:36:23,780
I propose that
we give them a round of applause.

822
00:36:23,980 --> 00:36:25,460
Let's wish the newlyweds

823
00:36:25,460 --> 00:36:27,020
live a long,

824
00:36:27,020 --> 00:36:28,980
harmonious and beautiful life

825
